race.comment: LAST SPLASH (1) shapes well for this on his sharp win a few runs back, getting around this track over 600m in 34.86 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Should be in this for a long way. KIWI MAKAVELI (3) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (30.16), beaten 3 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Key player if finds best. BUCKLE UP TAJA (5) was below best latest but did hit the frame in quick time two back when second (29.87) at this track in a Grade 3/4. Can improve sharply here. BUCKLE UP ARIA (2) can run a bold race on best form.
